  Locus:
    Page: 173
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Freedom
---
He only has freedom who ideally loves freedom himself and is glad to extend
it to others. He who cares to have slaves must chain himself to them. He
who builds walls to create exclusion for others, builds walls across his
own freedom.
